snippet.textDisplay:
Have listened to this song a long ago. But never felt the music, the words...

today, when Atif Aslam sang this song live in front of 35-40k people in Bangladesh at Magical Nights 2.0, I had goosebumps. 
just closed my eyes, and felt like, this night, this song should never end. 
But every great things comes to an end. And here I am, sitting alone at my bedroom, staring at the sky , listening to this song on repeat. I feel so full
